Solution ->
1) Create object of Reentrant lock and initialize it.
2) After creating whereever you want to use this lock then use lock.lock() where first lock is variable name and another lock() is method present in reentrant lock.
3) Inside try block write your logic, in this code we have written logic for money withdrawl.
4) Don't forget to release lock in finally block otherwise it will be a situatution like deadlock.
5) END